body:
BTS Reaction: You listen to German rap

Anon requested: Hi 👋🏻 could you please write a BTS or NCT reaction to their s/o listening to German rap? I‘ve recently discovered German rap and love it :D

A/N: I listened to some German rap before writing this and I can definitely see all of the boys liking it! I haven’t mentioned any specific songs or artists in these reactions to keep it generic but this is the song I would recommend!


Seokjin

You would be sat at your desk with your earphones on engrossed in your studies when Jin would creep up behind you and place his hands on his shoulders causing you to shriek. He would be chuckling at your reaction as you would take off your earphones. 

‘What are you listening to so loud that you couldn’t hear me come in?’ He would ask as he pulls up a chair and sat next to you.

You’d reply 'German rap,’ and hand him your earphones so he could list. He would bop his head to the music. You would go to take your headphones back but he would brush your hand away playfully and carry on listening to your playlist as he went on his phone. You would just go back to studying and accept that you wouldn’t be getting your earphones back any time soon.

Yoongi

Yoongi would be on his laptop when you would go over and play a German rap song you had found earlier that day from your phone. He’d question what it was and you would tell him the name of the song. He would nod his head and seem impressed but would pass your phone back to you and go back on his laptop. You’d feel disappointed, it would be rare to find a song that he liked or one he hadn’t already heard. So when you walk away and look back to see him typing the name of the song into his laptop, you wouldn’t be able to help but smile to yourself.

Hoseok

Your friend would have rung you up telling you she was unable to go to the concert for the German rap artist you had been excited to see for weeks. The disappointment etched on your face would be obvious because Hoseok would ask you what’s wrong. You’d tell him and he would instantly insist on going with you.

Throughout the concert you would both be dancing and just having the best time (who wouldn’t love going to a concert with Hoseok pls).

After the concert, you would thank him for coming with you and he would wrap his arm around your shoulders and beam, asking you if there were any other concerts coming up and insist on going to them all because he had that much fun.  

Namjoon

Namjoon would ask you if you had any song recommendations as he wanted to post one on Twitter but couldn’t think of any songs he wanted to share. You hesitantly play him a German rap song that you thought he would like. He would listen and not say anything for a while leaving you nervous about what he thinks. Before long, he’d be tapping on his phone and you would assume he had got bored of the song and resumed finding another. But you’d receive a notification on your phone seeing he had tweeted the song you’d shown him. ‘Thanks babe.’ He’d say as he would kiss the top of your head.

Jimin

You’d take Jimin to a party your friends were hosting so he could finally meet them and because Jimin will take any opportunity to drink. You and Jimin would be sitting on the sofas with some of your friends drinking and talking when one of your friends would play a German rap song and you’d recognise it instantly. You, slightly intoxicated, would cheer ‘this is one of my favourite songs!’ and rap some of the lyrics you knew with your friends. Jimin, unaware you knew any rap songs, let alone German rap, would be impressed and ask you to play him the song later.

Taehyung

You would be driving with Taehyung in the passenger’s seat on your way to get food, when a German rap song would come on your playlist. Before you could even react, Tae would clap his hands and smile that boxy smile you love exclaiming ‘I love this song Y/N! How do you know it?’ And you would both share how you came across the song whilst jamming in the car and playing other songs that you each liked.

Jungkook

Jungkook would be out running some errands so you would take the opportunity of being home alone to blast your music loudly. You would be unaware that Jungkook had returned home leaning against the doorframe of the kitchen watching you dance and rap along to some of the lyrics of the German rap song you’d be playing as you cleaned. You’d turn around and jump when you see him standing there and instantly blush from being caught. He would ease your embarrassment though by dancing himself (like the gif no doubt) and you’d both continue cleaning whilst dancing stupidly.

summary: i see u is a bts fan 👀 have u typed the members? i agree with hobi being an esfj and tae being an enfp from that mbti quiz they...
question: i see u is a bts fan 👀 have u typed the members? i agree with hobi being an esfj and tae being an enfp from that mbti quiz they took
answer:
kinda….. I have a hard time typing kpop idols because so much of what they show is fake as hell or just not useful for typing but i have a vague idea lol. while I have been a fan of them for a few years now, lately I just listen to their music so this is all based off of content from like 2013-early 2017ish.
those mbti results were so wrong tho oh god I mean YOONGI…. AN INFP….. ARE YOU KIDDING

Jin: xSFJ, the fact that he got INTP in that test is just more proof that tests are garbage lmao. gives me p6w7 vibes? or has that as a fix. sp/so.

Yoongi: IxTJ, lately I’ve been leaning towards ISTJ. I originally typed him as sp/sx but idk, he’s definitely an sp dom though. probably a 5. 513?

Hoseok: ESFJ, probably so/sp, 2 fix and maybe 1

Namjoon: INFJ, DEFINITELY sx blind. sp/so?? probably a 9w1? 945 tritype but idk the order

Jimin: ENFJ 2w3 or 3w2. 6 fix? maybe so/sx.

Taehyung: the biggest ExFP ive ever seen, probably ESFP tbh but I could see arguments for ENFP. I was thinking he’s a so/sx but I could also see sx blind. 7 fix.

Jungkook: HE’S SUCH AN ISFP this is the type I’m most sure about. definitely has sp somewhere, 4 and 7 fixes and maybe 9

title: dating yoongi
body:
A/N: Jin version here ✨  Others coming soon!

  • such a softie
  • was quiet and shy when you first met him 
  • before he spoke to you, you didn’t even really know he existed 
  • he came up to you and offered to buy you your coffee 
  • his tone of voice was flat and dull but his face showed real signs of happiness 
  • gummy smile made your knees weak 
  • got to know each other pretty fast 
  • you fell in love with his personality 
  • very open minded and you loved that 
  • both very compatible and similar people 
  • from day one he told you that he wasn’t great at expressing himself and his feelings 
  • he was worried it would make you distance yourself, 
  • but you made him the happiest boy in the world by sticking by his side no matter what
  • despite his expressionless manner, he always showed you how he loves you in small ways 
  • eg he literally got a crate of your favourite flowers shipped to you just because you had one bad day
  • would kill you if you ever told the boys how soft and whipped he was for you 
  • would literally do anything for you
  • lots songs and raps written for you/dedicated to you as a way for showing his love for you 
  • you would bring him coffee while he was working in the studio 
  • he usually wouldn’t allow people in there while he was working bc it distracts him except from you
  • he would need you there for inspiration and motivation 
  • you always found him there whenever you were upset, 
  • he would hug you and let you cry on his shoulder
  • wouldn’t care about his shirt getting ruined as long as he could make you feel better 
  • one of the only people who could cheer you up successfully 
  • would tell you to “wait there” while he ran out to buy you ice cream and a teddy bear 
  • not that much of a cuddly person 
  • but could never say no to you when you asked for a hug 
  • just wanted the best for you 
  • he would be in no rush to get married and process the relationship 
  • and you understood that 
  • most girls would want a ring on their finger but you were both happy right now and that was all that matters 
  • despite the fact that he would be in no rush for marriage, you spoke about it frequently 
  • he hoped to have a musical child with you 
  • constantly told you what a fantastic mother you would be 
  • and you told him what a great father he would be 
  • he couldn’t wait to spend the rest of his life with you 
  • was confident you were the one for him

- ‘I’m confused but I love it’

summary: Dear Bangtan, From Seoul, Fukuoka, Kyocera dome, to fanmeeting, last tour I tried my best to see you boys perform as much as i...
caption:
Dear Bangtan,
From Seoul, Fukuoka, Kyocera dome, to fanmeeting, last tour I tried my best to see you boys perform as much as i could. It was a great year and a beautiful memory for me. Supporting you guys gave me strength and hope ☺️
Now that you guys are about to start a new world tour, I hope you guys can finish it healthily and successfully (I hope I get to go to ly world tour too~ I’ll be waiting. Fighting!💕)
Happy 5 years anniversary Bangtan! Cheers for more years to come~
